<problem id="fs-id1171472316658">
<para id="fs-id1171472089480">Is citizen engagement necessary for a democracy to function? Explain.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1171474500609">
<problem id="fs-id1171474394059">
<para id="fs-id1171474402145">Which is the more important reason for being engaged: to gain power or improve the quality of life? Why?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1171474372999">
<problem id="fs-id1171474420146">
<para id="fs-id1171474194684">Are all Americans equally able to become engaged in government? What factors make it more possible for some people to become engaged than others? What could be done to change this?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
